(213, 'DIMNESS OF VISION CURE BY -  PERMANENT, EASY, SAFE, FAST & COST EFFECTIVE TREATMENT', 'DIMNESS OF VISION CURE BY -  EASY, SAFE, FAST & COST EFFECTIVE TREATMENT CURE                                                                                     Dim vision can be caused by an assortment of eye conditions, and patients should seek treatment if they notice dimming in their visual field. It can be a sign of an acute ocular condition that needs immediate treatment. An ophthalmologist can examine the patient, determine the cause, and recommend some treatments to address it. Patients with a history of vision problems should make sure their doctors know about it when they seek care for dimmer than normal vision.\nSometimes the issue is infection or inflammation in the eye and around the optic nerve. Inflammation of the eyelids and neighboring structures can also cause dim vision, as can a foreign body in the eye. The patient may also notice eye pain, headaches, and a discharge from the eye in these cases. Blurred vision can also occur, and sometimes swelling narrows the eyes to slits and makes it hard to see.\n\nDR ARPIT CHOPRA (MD HOMOEOPATHY)\nChief Consultant Homoeopath & Biochemic\nAAROGYA SUPERSPECIALITY MODERN HOMOEOPATHIC CLINIC(Computerised)\n102, First Floor, Krishna Tower, Opposite Curewell\nHospital, Newpalasia, Indore (M.P.)\nMob 9713092737 /  9713037737/ 9907527914(whats up no)\nPH - 0731-2532737, 3961737\nwebsite- www.homoeopathycure.com For more info visit us at http://aarogyahomoeopathyindore.com/bizFloat/597c619e3745c7052c839237/DIMNESS-OF-VISION-CURE-BY-COMPLETE-PERMANENT-EASY-SAFE-FAST-COSTEFFECTIVE-PERMANENT-MODERN-HOMOEOPATHY-CURE-Dim-vision-can-be-caused-by-an-assortment-of-eye-conditions-and-patients-should-seek-treatme', 1, 'https://atzean.com/arogya-wp/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/170.webp', '', '2023-01-30 12:20:01', '2023-01-30 12:20:01', 'DIMNESS OF VISION CURE BY -  PERMANENT, EASY, SAFE, FAST & COST EFFECTIVE TREATMENT', '', '', '', ''