(24, 1, '424', '470', 'Kidney', 'The kidneys are a vital organ in the body responsible for filtering waste and excess fluids. When the kidneys become damaged or diseased, it can lead to serious health problems.', '<p>Kidney Treatments, Problems and Solutions</p>\r\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong>:</p>\r\n<p>The kidneys are a vital organ in the body responsible for filtering waste and excess fluids. When the kidneys become damaged or diseased, it can lead to serious health problems. Homeopathy is a form of alternative medicine that uses natural substances to stimulate the body\'s healing response. In this article, we will discuss kidney treatments, problems and solutions in homeopathy.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kidney Problems:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Acute Nephritis:</strong> This is an inflammation of the kidneys that can be caused by a bacterial or viral infection. Symptoms include fever, abdominal pain, and changes in urine color.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chronic Nephritis:</strong> This is a long-term inflammation of the kidneys that can lead to kidney damage and eventually kidney failure. Symptoms include fatigue, swelling, and changes in urine output.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Kidney Stones:</strong> These are hard deposits of minerals and acid salts that can form in the kidneys. Symptoms include severe pain in the back or side, nausea, and blood in the urine.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Glomerulonephritis:</strong> This is an inflammation of the tiny filters in the kidneys called glomeruli. It can be caused by an autoimmune disorder or a bacterial infection. Symptoms include blood in the urine, swelling, and high blood pressure.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Homeopathic Solutions:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>ApisMellifica:</strong> This remedy is useful for acute nephritis with symptoms of burning pain in the kidneys, fever, and a swollen face.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Berberis Vulgaris: </strong>This remedy is useful for chronic nephritis with symptoms of pain in the kid