 By using highly diluted preparations of natural substances, homeopathy can stimulate the body\'s own healing response and alleviate symptoms. While homeopathy should not be used in place of conventional medical treatment, it can be used in conjunction with it to.</p>', 'Read More', 'hepato gastroenterology', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 09:31:16', '2023-05-23 17:08:57'),
